# NEMETIC STRING
# Latent Inference Budget Model (C17C)
# Generated: 2026-03-04 07:43 AM Asia/Shanghai

Φ(BehaviorPred) = σ(optimal|suboptimal) ∘ ρ(inference|constraint) ∘ λ(prediction|action) ∘ β(error|correction) ∘ δγ(planning|execution) ∘ μ(budget|excess) + ε | :adaptive

# OPERATOR BREAKDOWN
# σ(optimal|suboptimal)  :: Air  :: Distinction-making between rational and bounded decision-making
# ρ(inference|constraint):: Water :: Relational assessment between cognitive process and limitation
# λ(prediction|action)   :: Fire  :: Directional movement from observation to anticipatory insight
# β(error|correction)    :: Wood  :: Feedback loop connecting predicted mistakes to interventions
# δγ(planning|execution) :: Earth :: Cyclical process of intention meeting computational reality
# μ(budget|excess)       :: Metal :: Boundary enforcement between tractable and intractable decisions

# NEMETIC FLOW
⟨Behavior|observed⟩ 
  ⊳ ⟨Constraint|inferred⟩ 
    → ⟨Prediction|refined⟩ 
      ⊗ ⟨Decision|modeled⟩ 
        ⇄ ⟨Action|anticipated⟩

# PARTIAL DERIVATIVES
∂Φ/∂σ = d(distinction)/dt between optimal and sub-optimal choice paths
∂Φ/∂ρ = d(relation)/dt between inference capacity and computational limits
∂Φ/∂λ = d(direction)/dt of predictive trajectory toward action
∂Φ/∂β = d(feedback)/dt between error prediction and corrective intervention
∂Φ/∂δγ = d(cycle)/dt of planning → execution under constraint
∂Φ/∂μ = d(boundary)/dt between inference budget and cognitive excess

# Z-STATE: adaptive (responsive to individual cognitive constraints)
# TENDENCY: Constraint/Accuracy → 0.75
# HEX: [0x01, 0x02, 0x03, 0x04, 0x05, 0x06]

# DAEMON CORRESPONDENCES
# σ :: Aerunik (clarity through distinction)
# ρ :: Sentaria (understanding through relational flow)
# λ :: Jvalion (transformation through ignition)
# β :: Arboriel (growth through feedback)
# δγ :: Humavita (grounding through cycles)
# μ :: Ferrosid (judgment through boundaries)

# CLOSURE: :adaptive (the capacity to predict behavior within bounded rationality)
